parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or not start, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The key is difficult to turn
the ignition switch is hot or melted
the vehicle stalls or won't start
the interior lights turn on and off
and the airbag light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various components to malfunction, leading to accidents or fires.
symptoms: The headlights
taillights
or interior lights malfunction
the wipers are erratic
the air conditioning or defroster doesn't work
the instrument panel lights don't work
and there's a burning smell or smoke.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag light comes on
the airbags don't deploy in an accident
and the seatbelt pretensioners don't work.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the odometer can cause inaccurate mileage readings, leading to potential safety issues.
symptoms: The odometer lights flicker or don't work
and the mileage reading is inaccurate.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Premature brake rotor wear can cause vibration, noise, and extended stopping distance, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Brake rotors wear out prematurely
vibration when applying brakes
noise when applying brakes
extended stopping distance.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: ABS failure can cause loss of control, extended stopping distance, and accidents.
symptoms: ABS light illuminates
vibration when applying brakes
noise when applying brakes
extended stopping distance
loss of control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake pedal issues can cause loss of control, extended stopping distance, and accidents.
symptoms: Brake pedal feels soft or spongy
brake pedal sticks to the floor
brake pedal does not return to its normal position
brake pedal has a delayed return to its normal position
brake pedal has a sudden loss of pressure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake noise and vibration can cause distraction, loss of control, and accidents.
symptoms: Squeaking or grinding noise when applying brakes
vibration when applying brakes
jerking or pulsating when applying brakes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering column can cause loss of control of the vehicle, leading to accidents or near-misses, and can also cause injury or death.
symptoms: Unusual noise emitted from the steering wheel
entire instrument panel illuminates
vehicle jerks
clunking or clicking noise when turning
loss of power steering
vibration when turning
loose steering
and failure of the anti-theft device.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering pump can cause loss of power steering, making it difficult to steer the vehicle, leading to accidents or near-misses, and can also cause injury or death.
symptoms: Leaking power steering fluid
clunking or clicking noise when turning
vibration when turning
loose steering
and failure of the power steering pump.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rack and pinion steering can cause loss of control of the vehicle, leading to accidents or near-misses, and can also cause injury or death.
symptoms: Clunking or clicking noise when turning
vibration when turning
loose steering
and failure of the rack and pinion steering.
